snippet.title: Circuit Breakers - Shoot All Robots Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Shoot all robots in early 2017, when Circuit Breakers comes to PS4. Choose from an array of characters, each with their own unique weapons, and team up with friends in local co-op play. Follow us on Twitter (https://twitter.com/ShootAllRobots) and Facebook (https://www.facebook.com/Circuit-Breakers-661312577379842/?ref=aymt_homepage_panel) for updates.
